* 0.0.93: (alpha 3)
	- Use constant instant of string in Database class to speed up
	- Implement Copy/Cut/Paste (interracting with X Cut Buffer)
	- <Enter> on edit field of dialog will issue Accept command
	- Allow setting Vdesk's system hotkey/button (default: Ctrl+RightClick)
	- Fixed vdesk crash when loading big apps (OO, Mozilla, Opera...)
	- Use $LDFLAGS

* 0.0.92: (alpha 2)
	- Add Screen capture
	- Add shadow for menu & dialogs
	- Add adaptive text color
	- Allow edit link
	- Allow using <Tab> to switch to other control in Linke Editor,
	using <Esc> to close, using <Spacebar> & <Enter> with Buttons
	- Add background manager (auto change background image)
	- Fixed "dirty" icon text
	- Fixed mouse leave icon text bug
	- Check file name/caption before save to link

* 0.0.91: (alpha 1)
	- Fixed some bugs
	- Add default icon/icon path

* 0.0.90: (Initial release - alpha)
	- Rewrite all idesk's components
	- Add link editor dialog
	- Add popup menu for icon
	- Add device link
